{"tid":1807654,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"屯門2匪冒警截查　強搶六旬漢21萬現金","createTime":"2020-01-02T02:40:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-20T05:26:02.000Z","uid":139744,"like":52,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"2dd632b990b237c5f7b01f72e70c719306c89559","tid":1807654,"uid":139744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T02:40:43.000Z","msg":"便衣+唔出示委任証 成新常態既後果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今日(1月1日)傍晚6時許，一名姓黃(63歲)男子，途經屯門警署100米外的建榮街25號，突遭2名自稱警員的男子截停，要求查閱身份證。黃見對方身形強壯如電視劇的警察般，即使<span style=\"color: red;\">對方沒有出示委任證件亦不虞有詐配合調查。<br />\n期間，對方突然搶走事主內有21萬港元現金的紙袋，旋即轉身逃去。黃此時才如夢初醒，察覺對方並非警員</span>，截查他是企圖搶劫，他試圖追截不果，無奈報警求助。<br />\n警方經初步調查後，把案件列作冒警及盜竊，交由屯門警區刑事調查隊跟進，正追緝2名涉案的冒警男子，他們年約30歲、身高約1.7米；其中一人身材強壯及蓄短黑髮，案發時身穿綠色外套及藍色長褲；另一人中等身材，案發時身穿黑色長袖上衣及長褲。"},{"pid":"d2140ca4f59023c7082e5f2a0614691108b38a1a","tid":1807654,"uid":139744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T02:41:07.000Z","msg":"Source: <a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200101/bkn-20200101231151655-0101_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200101%2Fbkn-20200101231151655-0101_00822_001.html&d=navV%2BA4%2FMRIetR8KyPOOAC%2F0jIrp0bHqVoz25JuQVd4%3D&h=3e9912b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200101/bkn-20200101231151655-0101_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"d739f4e2b08fc91abd14bd8b1fec16dc12a1f3f8","tid":1807654,"uid":37413,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T04:41:06.000Z","msg":"未必冒㗎，可能真呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de70b8008dce5ae61c53cb881a4d840e333bc3fd","tid":1807654,"uid":5289,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T04:41:54.000Z","msg":"佢地係 懷疑警察"},{"pid":"4b5c16c86a78a56f074fcf5686a8749d728ebbe0","tid":1807654,"uid":139744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T04:52:2